trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemDeleted"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemDeleted"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemDeleted> event when a Delete button (a button with its `CommandName` property set to "Delete") within the control is clicked, but after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control deletes the record.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontrollere hever den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemDeleted>-hendelse når en Slett-knapp (en knapp med den `CommandName` egenskapen satt til "Delete") i kontrollen klikkes, men når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontrollen sletter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemDeleted> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>

trans-unit.source: This allows you to provide an event handler that performs a custom routine, such as checking the results of a delete operation, whenever this event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at du må oppgi en hendelsesbehandling som utfører en egendefinert rutine, for eksempel kontrollere resultatet av en sletting når denne hendelsen oppstår.

trans-unit.source: A DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs object is passed to the event handler, which allows you to determine the number of records affected and any exceptions that might have occurred.
trans-unit.target: En DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs-objekt er sendt til hendelsesbehandlingen, som gjør det mulig å bestemme antall poster som er påvirket, og eventuelle unntak som kan ha oppstått.

trans-unit.source: To determine the number of records affected by the delete operation, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For å fastsette antall poster som er berørt av sletteoperasjonen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A> property to determine whether any exceptions occurred.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A>til å fastslå om unntak oppstod.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also indicate whether the exception was handled in the event handler by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også angi om unntaket ble behandlet i behandlingsprogrammet ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to access the name/value pairs of the key fields and non-key fields of the deleted record, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Keys%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Values%2A> properties, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha tilgang til navn/verdi-par med feltene nøkkelfelt og ikke er en nøkkel i slettet post, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Keys%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Values%2A>Egenskaper henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Values%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Keys%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling events, see [NIB: Consuming Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om behandling av hendelser [NIB: bruker hendelser](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67).

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of the DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs class, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: En liste med opprinnelige verdier for en forekomst av klassen DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs, kan du se den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å initialisere en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser første egenskapsverdiene for en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: |Property|Initial value| |--------------|-------------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A>|The value of the `affectedRows` parameter.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A>|The <xref:System.Exception?displayProperty=fullName> contained in the `e` parameter.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>|Initialized to `false`.| > [!NOTE] > This constructor is used primarily by control developers when raising events.
trans-unit.target: | Egenskapen | Standardverdi | |--------------|-------------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A>| Verdien for den `affectedRows` parameteren. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A>| <xref:System.Exception?displayProperty=fullName>Finnes i den `e` parameteren. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>| Initialisert til `false`. | > [!NOTE] > Denne konstruktøren brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere ved å heve hendelser.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A> </xref:System.Exception?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A>

trans-unit.source: The number of rows affected by the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: Antall rader som er berørt av sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Exception> that represents the exception raised when the delete operation was performed.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Exception>som representerer det oppstod et unntaket under sletteoperasjonen ble utført.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: If no exception is raised, use <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> for this parameter.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen unntak oppstår, kan du bruke <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> for denne parameteren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of rows affected by the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: Henter hvor mange rader som er berørt av sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Use the AffectedRows property to determine the number of rows affected by the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: Bruk AffectedRows-egenskapen til å finne ut hvor mange rader som påvirkes av sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: This value is commonly used to verify that the appropriate number of rows was deleted.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien brukes vanligvis til å bekrefte at riktig antall rader ble slettet.

trans-unit.source: The number of rows affected by the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: Antall rader som er berørt av sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the exception (if any) that was raised during the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: Henter unntaket (Hvis noen) som oppstod under sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Exception property to determine the exception (if any) that was raised during the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: Bruk unntak-egenskapen til å fastslå unntaket (Hvis noen) som oppstod under sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: If no exceptions were raised, this property returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen unntak oppstod, denne egenskapen returnerer `null`.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If an exception was raised and you decide to handle the exception in the event handler, be sure to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A> property to `true`; otherwise, the exception is passed to the next method on the call stack for handling.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis det oppstod et unntak, og du vil behandle unntak i hendelsesbehandlingen, må du angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>egenskapen `true`; ellers unntaket er sendt til neste metode i kallstakken for behandling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Exception> that represents the exception that was raised during the delete operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Exception>som representerer unntak oppstod under sletteoperasjonen.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether an exception that was raised during the delete operation was handled in the event handler.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om et unntak som oppstod under sletteoperasjonen ble behandlet i behandlingsprogram.

trans-unit.source: When an exception is raised during the delete operation, use the ExceptionHandled property to indicate whether the exception was handled in the event handler.
trans-unit.target: Bruk egenskapen ExceptionHandled som viser om unntaket ble behandlet i behandlingsprogrammet når det oppstår et unntak under sletteoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: When this property is set to `true`, the exception is considered handled and is not passed further up the call stack.
trans-unit.target: Når denne egenskapen er satt til `true`, unntaket regnes håndtert og er ikke sendt flere opp kallstakken.

trans-unit.source: If this property is set to `false`, the exception is passed to the next method on the call stack for handling.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen settes til `false`, unntaket er sendt til neste metode i kallstakken for behandling.

trans-unit.source: To determine which exception was raised, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk til å fastslå hvilke unntak oppstod i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Exception%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the exception was handled in the event handler; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis unntaket ble behandlet i behandlingsprogrammet; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets an ordered dictionary of key field name/value pairs that contains the names and values of the key fields of the deleted items.
trans-unit.target: Henter en bestilte ordliste for nøkkelfeltet navn/verdi-par som inneholder navn og verdier av nøkkelfeltene for slettede elementer.

trans-unit.source: Use the Keys property to access the values of the key fields for the record to delete.
trans-unit.target: Bruke egenskapen nøkler å få tilgang til verdiene i nøkkelfeltene for posten som skal slettes.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use these values to keep a log of deleted records.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel bruke disse verdiene for å loggføre slettede poster.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This property contains only the key fields.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Inneholder bare nøkkelfeltene for denne egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: To access the non-key fields, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Values%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha tilgang til feltene ikke er en nøkkel, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Values%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Values%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Keys property returns an object that implements the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> interface.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen nøkler returnerer et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>

trans-unit.source: The object contains <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> objects that represent the key fields of the record to delete.
trans-unit.target: Objektet inneholder <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>objekter som representerer nøkkelfeltene for oppføringen for å slette.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > As a shortcut, you can also use the indexer of the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> object to access the field values directly.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Som en snarvei du kan også bruke indeksering av den <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>objekt for å få tilgang til feltet verdier direkte.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"></xref> that contains an ordered dictionary of key field name/value pairs used to match the item to delete.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"> </xref> som inneholder en bestilte ordliste for nøkkelfeltet navn/verdi-par brukes til å samsvare med elementet skal slettes.

trans-unit.source: Gets a dictionary of the non-key field name/value pairs for the item to delete.
trans-unit.target: Henter en ordliste for ikke-nøkkelfelt navn/verdi-par for elementet skal slettes.

trans-unit.source: Use the Values property to access the values of the non-key fields for the record to delete.
trans-unit.target: Bruk egenskapen verdier å få tilgang til verdiene i feltene ikke er en nøkkel for posten som skal slettes.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use these values to keep a log of deleted records.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel bruke disse verdiene for å loggføre slettede poster.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This property does not contain the key fields for the record.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Egenskapen inneholder ikke nøkkelfeltene for oppføringen.

trans-unit.source: To access the key fields, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Keys%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha tilgang til nøkkelfeltene, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Keys%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewDeletedEventArgs.Keys%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Values property returns an <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> object that implements the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> interface.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer verdiene en <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> </xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>

trans-unit.source: The object contains <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> objects that represent the non-key fields of the record to delete.
trans-unit.target: Objektet inneholder <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>objekter som representerer feltene ikke er en nøkkel for oppføringen for å slette.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > As a shortcut, you can also use the indexer of the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> object to access the field values directly.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Som en snarvei du kan også bruke indeksering av den <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>objekt for å få tilgang til feltet verdier direkte.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"></xref> that contains a dictionary of the non-key field name/value pairs for the item to delete.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"> </xref> som inneholder en liste over ikke-nøkkelfelt navn/verdi-par for elementet skal slettes.
